node.text: We are hiring…. We are excited to hire a few people to our growing team. Please contact us if you are interested.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 18, 2021.

node.text: Love this pink Moroccan rug.. this hand made Mrirt rug is 9’10” x 14 available at our new showroom in Norwalk Connecticut

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 15, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Berber necklaces are one of my favorite decor pieces from Morocco, the history and beauty of the necklace makes a amazing art piece.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 14, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text: Custom made walnut table made by Patrick… 💙💙💙

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 13, 2021.

node.text: New showroom is open now Wednesday thur Saturdays from 10-4pm

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'NEW WAREHOUSE IS OPEN AT 345 WILSON AVE NORWALK CT'.

node.text: We are so excited for our new location being open… Can’t wait to see everyone.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 11, 2021.

node.text: We have large selection of the glass beads from Ghana in stock. We opening the new warehouse space tomorrow at 345 Wilson Ave on Norwalk, C…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 09, 2021.

node.text: We will be open again starting this Thursday from 10-4pm and the new address is 345 Wilson Ave Norwalk CT… can’t wait to see everyone…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 08, 2021.

node.text: Getting the new ware house in order we will be open Thursday no matter what shape we are in… we can’t wait to see everyone! And we are @mongersmarketusa today…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Knock On Wood / Home Decor on August 02, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text: Just delivered out this amazing table for @beinfieldarchitecture .. I love that the space between the boards casts a cool shadow on the floor.. such a amazing project.
